TER.TERInteractiveDecoder
Class InteractiveDecoder

java.lang.Object
  TER.TERInteractiveDecoder.InteractiveDecoder

public class InteractiveDecoder
extends java.lang.Object

Main class of TER interactive decoder application. It receives all parameters, checks its validity and runs TER interactive decoder. Usage example:
  construct
  setParameters
  run

Version:
2.0
Author:
Group on Interactive Coding of Images (GICI)
